艾莎一角因為呈現了多面、並有所演變的性格而受到影評界稱讚。娛樂網「{{lang|en|Collider.com}}」的麥特·郭德堡（{{lang|en|Matt Goldberg}}）將艾莎評論為「一位不凡而又惹人憐愛的角色」<ref>{{cite news|last=Goldberg|first=Matt|title=FROZEN Review|url=http://collider.com/frozen-review/|accessdate=2013-12-28|publisher=Collider.com|date=2013-11-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231033143/http://collider.com/frozen-review|archivedate=2013-12-31}}</ref>，《{{Link-en|印度第一郵報|First Post (India)}}》的迪潘加納·帕爾（{{lang|en|Deepanjana Pal}}）對於《冰雪奇緣》將艾莎重新改為正派角色的做法表示讚賞，並指出「艾莎不是像古怪、狠毒的『冰雪女王』那種壞心又冷酷的女性，她是一位身陷困境的恐慌姑娘，想要試著了解自己的能力、而且承受著外界期待和傳統的重擔。別人很容易就能同情她，並且在她蓋出壯觀的宮殿時對她的魔力感到驚奇」<ref name=Post>{{cite news|last=Pal|first=Deepanjana|title=Frozen review: This modern Snow Queen will melt your heart|url=http://www.firstpost.com/bollywood/frozen-review-this-modern-snow-queen-will-melt-your-heart-1257979.html|accessdate=2013-12-09|newspaper={{Link-en|印度第一郵報|First Post (India)|First Post}}|date=2013-11-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208102129/http://www.firstpost.com/bollywood/frozen-review-this-modern-snow-queen-will-melt-your-heart-1257979.html|archivedate=2013-12-08}}</ref>。[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]新聞網{{Link-en|Stuff.co.nz|Stuff.co.nz}}的詹姆斯·克魯特（{{lang|en|James Croot}}）將艾莎在忍辱下的自我流放比作《[[獅子王|獅子王]]》裡辛巴被逐出的遭遇<ref>{{cite news|last=Croot|first=James|title=Frozen is Disney at its best|url=http://www.stuff.co.nz/entertainment/film/film-reviews/9504728/Frozen-is-Disney-at-its-best|accessdate=2013-12-12|publisher={{Link-en|Stuff.co.nz|Stuff.co.nz}}|date=2013-12-12}}</ref>，《華爾街內幕》（{{lang|en|''Wall St. Cheat Sheet''}}）的評論員凱瑟琳·韋伯（{{lang|en|Katherine Webb}}）則表示艾莎拾起自信和個性的橋段「向那些替自己尋找公主當榜樣的小女孩們傳達了一項振奮人心的訊息」<ref>{{cite news|last=Webb|first=Katherine|title=4 Ways 'Frozen' Flips the Traditional Disney Script|url=http://wallstcheatsheet.com/stocks/4-ways-frozen-flips-the-traditional-disney-script.html/|accessdate=2013-12-12|newspaper=Wall St. Cheat Sheet|date=2013-12-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221032334/http://wallstcheatsheet.com/stocks/4-ways-frozen-flips-the-traditional-disney-script.html/|archivedate=2015-02-21}}</ref>。

[[愛荷華州|愛荷華州]]《雪松瀑布時報》（{{lang|en|''Cedar Falls Times''}}）的崔維茲·賓恩（{{lang|en|Travis Bean}}）認為冰魔力這項艾莎所屬的「個人特質」讓她有了自我意識、以及將自己孤立到王國遠方以免傷人的無私之心，而這讓低年齡層的觀眾更能對《冰雪奇緣》的劇情產生領會<ref>{{cite news|last=Bean|first=Travis|title=Frozen features fantasy, focuses on family values|url=http://www.communitynewspapergroup.com/cedar_falls_times/columnists/article_12ca29ce-6bee-11e3-ad42-001a4bcf887a.html|accessdate=2013-12-23|newspaper=Cedar Falls Times|date=2013-12-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104142654/http://www.communitynewspapergroup.com/cedar_falls_times/columnists/article_12ca29ce-6bee-11e3-ad42-001a4bcf887a.html|archivedate=2014-01-04}}</ref>。[[波士頓學院|波士頓學院]]學生報《{{Link-en|頂峰報|The Heights (newspaper)}}》的影評麥德蓮娜·拉克威茲（{{lang|en|Magdalena Lachowicz}}）指出艾莎與安娜的血肉之情是整部片中最重要的元素<ref>{{cite news|last=Lachowicz |first=Magdalena |title=Animated Film 'Frozen' Breaks Disney Princess Conventions |url=http://www.bcheights.com/arts-review/movie-reviews/animated-film-frozen-breaks-disney-princess-conventions-1.3127463#.UqfYg42x7IV |accessdate=2013-12-10 |newspaper=The Heights |date=2013-12-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213022242/http://www.bcheights.com/arts-review/movie-reviews/animated-film-frozen-breaks-disney-princess-conventions-1.3127463 |archivedate=2013-12-13 }}</ref>，而這點也是獲得《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》影評史帝芬·霍登（{{lang|en|Stephen Holden}}）喜愛之處，他認為姊-{}-妹對彼此的愛才能「融化艾莎那顆飽受驚嚇的冰封之心」，而不是男女之間的愛情<ref name=NYT>{{cite news|last=Holden|first=Stephen|title=From the Heat of Royal Passion, Poof! It’s Permafrost|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/27/movies/disneys-frozen-a-makeover-of-the-snow-queen.html?_r=0|accessdate=2013-12-09|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|date=2013-11-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131209114709/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/11/27/movies/disneys-frozen-a-makeover-of-the-snow-queen.html?_r=0|archivedate=2013-12-09}}</ref>。[[華盛頓特區|華盛頓特區]]《{{Link-en|基督郵報|Christian Post}}》的艾瑪·昆斯（{{lang|en|Emma Koonse}}）認為艾莎與安娜這對姊-{}-妹是「目前迪士尼最可愛也最有魅力的角色」<ref name=Koonse/>。

另有數位影評家在評論中表示艾莎比貴為首要角色的安娜更富有趣味。[[菲律賓|菲律賓]][[ABS-CBN公司|ABS-CBN媒體公司]]的作家佛烈德·郝生（{{lang|en|Fred Hawson}}）將艾莎形容為「一位非凡的角色，並因為自身所具的能力而擁有獨特而富趣的經歷」，並認為《冰雪奇緣》應該多著墨於她，而不是安娜<ref>{{cite news|last=Hawson |first=Fred |title=Review: Icy sentimentality in 'Frozen' |url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/lifestyle/12/10/13/review-icy-sentimentality-frozen |accessdate=2013-12-10 |newspaper=[[ABS-CBN|ABS-CBN]] |date=2013-12-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131210091123/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/lifestyle/12/10/13/review-icy-sentimentality-frozen |archivedate=2013-12-10 }}</ref>。[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]《{{Link-en|論壇快報|The Express Tribune}}》的薩姆拉·穆斯林（{{lang|en|Samra Muslim}}）認為艾莎的存在才讓觀眾能對該片如此「著迷成癮」，並指出「她的個性是如此複雜和令人憐惜，值得做更深入的探索，但劇情卻花了更多時間在兩姐-{}-妹間的關係、安娜這位活潑迷人的典型迪士尼女角——及她的約會對象上面，而不是分給充滿魅力的艾莎」 <ref>{{cite news|last=Muslim|first=Samra|title=Movie review: Frozen - winter is coming|url=http://tribune.com.pk/story/661918/movie-review-frozen-winter-is-coming/|accessdate=2014-02-18|newspaper={{Link-en|論壇快報|The Express Tribune|The Express Tribune}}|date=2014-01-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140214123608/http://tribune.com.pk/story/661918/movie-review-frozen-winter-is-coming/|archivedate=2014-02-14}}</ref>。

然而，也有評論對艾莎的外型提出負面批判，《{{Link-en|倫敦標準晚報|London Evening Standard}}》的夏綠蒂·歐蘇利文（{{lang|en|Charlotte O'Sullivan}}）表示艾莎「很像選秀節目《[[X音素|X音素]]》中那些尖刻的評委，紫色眼影、瘦腰和小腳」<ref>{{cite news|last=O'Sullivan|first=Charlotte|title=Frozen 3D - film review|url=http://www.standard.co.uk/goingout/film/frozen-3d--film-review-8987794.html|accessdate=2013-12-10|newspaper={{Link-en|倫敦標準晚報|London Evening Standard|London Evening Standard}}|date=2013-12-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217205340/http://www.standard.co.uk/goingout/film/frozen-3d--film-review-8987794.html|archivedate=2013-12-17}}</ref>，《[[衛報|衛報]]》的安娜·史密斯（{{lang|en|Anna Smith}}）也表示自己不喜歡讓艾莎和安娜畫得像傳統迪士尼公主一樣，身材纖細、眼睛又過大<ref>{{cite news|last=Smith|first=Anna|title=Frozen in time: when will Disney's heroines reflect real body shapes?|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2013/nov/28/frozen-disney-female-body-image|accessdate=2013-12-15|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2013-11-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216023350/http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2013/nov/28/frozen-disney-female-body-image|archivedate=2013-12-16}}</ref>。

==== 《放開手》 ====
伊迪娜·曼佐也因為擔任艾莎的配唱而獲得許多讚譽，英國影評網{{lang|en|''Cine Vue''}}的阿蒙·瓦曼（{{lang|en|Amon Warmann}}）表示曼佐的嗓音「在這些歌謠中完美地遨翔」<ref>{{cite news|last=Warmann|first=Amon|title=Film Review: 'Frozen'|url=http://www.cine-vue.com/2013/12/film-review-frozen.html|accessdate=2013-12-10|newspaper=Cine Vue|date=2013-12-05|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207233359/http://www.cine-vue.com/2013/12/film-review-frozen.html|archivedate=2013-12-07}}</ref>，許多評論家尤其集中於她在《放開手》一曲中的表現，《[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]》的馬克·史奈提格（{{lang|en|Marc Snetiker}}）將這首艾莎在決定不再畏懼自己的力量時，所唱出的歌形容為「一首出色的解放頌曲」<ref name=EW2>{{cite news|last=Sneitker|first=Marc|title=Disney's 'Frozen' soundtrack: Ranking all nine original songs|url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2013/11/30/disney-frozen-soundtrack-ranking/|accessdate=2013-12-10|newspaper=Entertainment Weekly|date=2013-11-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131209024514/http://popwatch.ew.com/2013/11/30/disney-frozen-soundtrack-ranking/|archivedate=2013-12-09}}</ref>，許多評論紛紛以「電力四射」稱讚這一幕的曼佐<ref name=Das>{{cite news|last=Das|first=Lina|title=Idina Menzel: A snow queen to melt our hearts|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-2513887/Idina-Menzel-star-Broadway-snow-queen-melt-hearts.html|accessdate=2013-12-12|newspaper=Daily Mail|date=2013-11-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131207233756/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/home/you/article-2513887/Idina-Menzel-star-Broadway-snow-queen-melt-hearts.html|archivedate=2013-12-07}}</ref>，《[[多倫多星報|多倫多星報]]》的琳達·巴納德（{{lang|en|Linda Barnard}}）於評論中指出「在曼佐的強力歌喉之下，冰錐也會破碎成粉」<ref>{{cite news|last=Barnard|first=Linda|title=Frozen will warm your heart: review|url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/2013/11/27/animated_frozen_will_warm_your_heart_movie_review.html|accessdate=2013-12-14|newspaper=The Star|date=2013-11-27|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215093404/http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/movies/2013/11/27/animated_frozen_will_warm_your_heart_movie_review.html|archivedate=2013-12-15}}</ref>。

《{{Link-en|羅徹斯特城市報|City Newspaper|羅徹斯-{}-特城市報}}》的麥特·狄特拉克（{{lang|en|Matt DeTruck}}）寫道「曼佐實在功不可沒，她在歌唱中注入了最多的力道和激情，如同她飾演[[女巫前傳|其最有名的角色]]時一樣」<ref name="Rochester">{{cite news|last=DeTruck|first=Matt|title=CD Review: Disney's "Frozen" Soundtrack|url=http://www.rochestercitynewspaper.com/rochester/cd-review-disneys-frozen-soundtrack/Content?oid=2302643|accessdate=2013-12-10|newspaper=City Newspaper|date=2013-11-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203023510/http://www.rochestercitynewspaper.com/rochester/cd-review-disneys-frozen-soundtrack/Content?oid=2302643|archivedate=2013-12-03}}</ref>。《{{Link-en|愛爾蘭時報|Irish Times}}》的唐納德·克拉克（{{lang|en|Donald Clark}}）補充說「艾莎到冰河的出逃旅程催生了一首曲子，以充滿反抗精神的歌聲唱出了自立...《放開手》的兩段副歌後面都以一句略帶狡黠的『-{zh-cn:反正冰天雪地我也不怕; zh-hk:自信冷酷冷漠傷不到我; zh-tw:從不畏懼臣服冰霜風雪;}-』結尾。女孩，好樣的」<ref>{{cite news|last=Clark|first=Donald|title=Film review: Frozen|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/culture/film/film-review-frozen-1.1617850|accessdate=2013-12-14|newspaper=Irish Times|date=2013-12-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213171217/http://www.irishtimes.com/culture/film/film-review-frozen-1.1617850|archivedate=2013-12-13}}</ref>。《{{Link-en|牛津學生報|The Oxford Student}}》的納辛·艾索（{{lang|en|Nasim Asl}}）進一步寫道「曼佐藉《放開手》一曲的表演而在片中嶄露頭角，她那《女巫前傳》式的引吭高歌與冰宮平地起的非凡畫面搭配得相當完美，這確實展示出了迪士尼動畫的威力，而且兩者結合之後的歌曲，在所有動畫角色唱過的曲子當中也可視為有史以來最氣勢磅礡的一首」<ref>{{cite news|last=Asl|first=Nasim|title=Frozen Melts Viewers' Hearts|url=http://oxfordstudent.com/2013/12/13/frozen-melts-viewers-hearts/|accessdate=2013-12-15|newspaper=The Oxford Student|date=2013-12-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215233012/http://oxfordstudent.com/2013/12/13/frozen-melts-viewers-hearts/|archivedate=2013-12-15}}</ref>。

===獲獎===
2013年12月，艾莎和安娜均經[[女性電影記者聯盟|女性電影記者聯盟]]提名為最佳動畫女角，但數週後只有安娜入選<ref>{{cite news|title=2013 EDA Award Nominess|url=http://awfj.org/eda-awards/2013-eda-award-nominees/|accessdate=2013-12-17|newspaper=[[女性电影记者联盟|Alliance of Women Film Journalists]]|date=2013-12-11|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216223900/http://awfj.org/eda-awards/2013-eda-award-nominees/|archivedate=2013-12-16}}</ref>。儘管如此，艾莎仍在2013年度（第12屆）{{Link-en|視覺效果協會|Visual Effects Society|視覺效果協會獎}}中奪得「最佳動畫長片動畫角色」獎，她建出的冰宮獲頒該協會的「最佳動畫長片環境設計」獎、其召喚的暴風則拿下「最佳動畫長片模擬動畫效果」獎<ref>{{cite news|last=The Deadline Team|script-title=en:VES Awards: ‘Gravity’ Wins 6 Including Top Prize; ‘Frozen’ Goes 4-For-4; 3 Nods For ‘Game Of Thrones’|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/ves-award-winners-2014-visual-effects-society-awards/|accessdate=2014-02-13|newspaper=[[Deadline.com|Deadline]]|date=2014-02-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140213210219/http://www.deadline.com/2014/02/ves-award-winners-2014-visual-effects-society-awards/|archivedate=2014-02-13}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=S. Cohen|first=David|script-title=en:Visual Effects Society Awards: ‘Gravity’ Soars, ‘Frozen’ Sparkles|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/visual-effects-society-awards-live-coverage-1201100988/|accessdate=2014-02-13|newspaper=[[綜藝雜誌|Variety]]|date=2014-02-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140213094108/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/visual-effects-society-awards-live-coverage-1201100988/|archivedate=2014-02-13}}</ref>。而艾莎唱的主題曲《放開手》則獲頒[[奧斯卡金像獎|第86屆奧斯卡金像獎]]<ref>{{cite news|last=Staff|title=2013 Academy Awards Nominations and Winners by Category|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?view=allcategories&yr=2013&p=.htm|accessdate=2014-01-16|newspaper=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|date=2014-01-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228152810/http://boxofficemojo.com/oscar/chart/?view=allcategories&yr=2013&p=.htm|archivedate=2014-02-28}}</ref>、[[鳳凰城影評人協會|鳳凰城影評人協會獎]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://phoenixfilmcriticssociety.org/article/208/phoenix-film-critics-society-2013-award-nominations.html |title=Phoenix Film Critics Society 2013 Award Nominations |publisher=[[Phoenix_Film_Critics_Society|Phoenix Film Critics Society]] |accessdate=2013-12-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213143509/http://phoenixfilmcriticssociety.org/article/208/phoenix-film-critics-society-2013-award-nominations.html |archivedate=2013-12-13 }}</ref>、[[丹佛影評人協會|丹佛影評人協會獎]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Denver Film Critics Society Nominations|url=http://www.awardsdaily.com/blog/denver-film-critics-society-nominations/|accessdate=2014-01-06|newspaper=Awards Daily|date=2013-12-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107121933/http://www.awardsdaily.com/blog/denver-film-critics-society-nominations/|archivedate=2014-01-07}}</ref>的「最佳原創歌曲」獎，和[[廣播影評人協會|第19屆評論家選擇獎]]<ref name="hustle">{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/critics-choice-movie-awards-nominees-full-list/|title=American Hustle, 12 Years A Slave Lead BFCA’s Critics Choice Movie Awards Nominations|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2013-12-17|date=2013-12-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SoTeknMn?url=http://deadline.com/2013/12/critics-choice-movie-awards-nominees-full-list-652803/|archivedate=2014-09-23}}</ref>的「最佳歌曲」獎，此外也獲[[金球獎|第71屆金球獎]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Golden Globe Awards Nominations: '12 Years A Slave' & 'American Hustle' Lead Pack|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/golden-globe-awards-2014-nominations-full-list/|accessdate=2013-12-17|newspaper=Deadline|date=2013-12-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131216082358/http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/golden-globe-awards-2014-nominations-full-list/|archivedate=2013-12-16}}</ref>、[[衛星獎|第18屆衛星獎]]<ref>{{cite news|title=The International Press Academy Announces Nominations For The 18th Annual Satellite Awards™|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/the-international-press-academy-announces-nominations-for-the-18th-annual-satellite-awards-234075351.html|accessdate=2013-12-17|newspaper=PR Newswire|date=2013-12-02|author=International Press Academy|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131202183712/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/the-international-press-academy-announces-nominations-for-the-18th-annual-satellite-awards-234075351.html|archivedate=2013-12-02}}</ref>和[[休士頓影評人協會|休士頓影評人協會獎]]列入提名<ref>{{cite news|title=12 Years a Slave wins Pic, Cuaron Director for Houston Film Critics|url=http://www.awardsdaily.com/blog/12-years-a-slave-wins-pic-cuaron-director-for-houston-film-critics/|accessdate=2013-12-18|newspaper=Awards Daily|date=2013-12-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223093805/http://www.awardsdaily.com/blog/12-years-a-slave-wins-pic-cuaron-director-for-houston-film-critics|archivedate=2013-12-23}}</ref>。

