zel-vanellope-von-schweetz/|accessdate=2013-12-30|work=Inside the Magic|date=2013-11-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204122229/http://www.insidethemagic.net/2013/11/disney-infinity-finally-features-more-female-characters-in-new-toy-box-fun-with-frozen-rapunzel-vanellope-von-schweetz/|archivedate=2013-12-04}}</ref>。

===主題樂園===
在《冰雪奇緣》上映前的11月，[[華特迪士尼世界度假區|佛羅里達迪士尼]]和[[迪士尼樂園度假區|加州迪士尼]]兩座[[華特迪士尼樂園及度假區|主題樂園]]裡開始出現了由真人扮演、與遊客互動的的艾莎與安娜。佛州迪士尼園方也在[[艾波卡特|艾波卡特]]主題樂園區裡的{{Link-en|迪士尼挪威館|Norway (Epcot)|挪威館}}設立了遊憩景點，以表彰片中所用到的{{Link-en|挪威文化|Culture of Norway|挪威文化元素}}<ref>{{cite news|last=Brigante|first=Ricky|title=Anna and Elsa to begin "Frozen" character meet-and-greets at Walt Disney World and Disneyland in November|url=http://www.insidethemagic.net/2013/10/anna-and-elsa-to-begin-frozen-character-meet-and-greets-at-walt-disney-world-and-disneyland-in-november/|accessdate=2013-12-14|newspaper=Inside the Magic|date=2013-10-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214224801/http://www.insidethemagic.net/2013/10/anna-and-elsa-to-begin-frozen-character-meet-and-greets-at-walt-disney-world-and-disneyland-in-november/|archivedate=2013-12-14}}</ref>，而加州迪士尼則在[[幻想世界|幻想世界]]裡設置一座冬季主題屋<ref>{{cite news|last=Brigante|first=Ricky|title=Anna and Elsa joined by animated Olaf for 'Frozen' character meet-and-greet in Royal Reception at Disneyland|url=http://www.insidethemagic.net/2013/11/anna-and-elsa-joined-by-animated-olaf-for-frozen-character-meet-and-greet-in-royal-reception-at-disneyland/|accessdate=2013-12-14|newspaper=Inside the Magic|date=2013-11-15|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226105108/http://www.insidethemagic.net/2013/11/anna-and-elsa-joined-by-animated-olaf-for-frozen-character-meet-and-greet-in-royal-reception-at-disneyland/|archivedate=2014-02-26}}</ref>。[[巴黎迪士尼樂園|巴黎迪士尼樂園]]則在「魔幻遊行」（{{lang|en|''Disney Magic on Parade''}}）中各替艾莎、安娜和雪寶安排了一輛《冰雪奇緣》主題花車<ref>{{cite news|last=Lee|first=Banks|title=Day two of filming for the 2013 Disney Parks Christmas Day Parade – Photos/Video|url=http://attractionsmagazine.com/day-two-filming-2013-disney-parks-christmas-day-parade-photosvideo/|accessdate=2013-12-14|work=Orlando Attractions Magazine|date=2013-12-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140223000603/http://attractionsmagazine.com/day-two-filming-2013-disney-parks-christmas-day-parade-photosvideo/|archivedate=2014-02-23}}</ref>。

艾莎所唱的《放開手》在[[迪士尼加州冒險樂園|迪士尼加州冒險樂園]]舉辦的、長達30分鐘的晚間秀「冬之夢」（{{lang|en|''Winter Dreams''}}）中成為重點表演曲目<ref>{{cite news|last=Barnes|first=Brooke|title=Boys Don't Run Away From These Princesses|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/02/movies/frozen-disneys-new-fairy-tale-is-no-2-at-box-office.html?_r=0|accessdate=2013-12-14|newspaper=New York Times|date=2013-12-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131208134809/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/02/movies/frozen-disneys-new-fairy-tale-is-no-2-at-box-office.html?_r=0|archivedate=2013-12-08}}</ref>，該項活動是冬季主題版本的「{{link-en|色彩世界|World of Color}}」，內容以展示迪士尼動畫或電影的音樂和聲光表演為主<ref>{{cite news|last=Brigante|first=Ricky|title=World of Color – Winter Dreams all-new nighttime Disneyland show debuts featuring Frozen, Toy Story, holiday songs|url=http://www.insidethemagic.net/2013/11/world-of-color-winter-dreams-all-new-nighttime-disneyland-show-debuts-featuring-frozen-toy-story-holiday-songs/|accessdate=2013-12-14|newspaper=Inside the Magic|date=2013-11-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214230742/http://www.insidethemagic.net/2013/11/world-of-color-winter-dreams-all-new-nighttime-disneyland-show-debuts-featuring-frozen-toy-story-holiday-songs/|archivedate=2013-12-14}}</ref>。巴黎迪士尼的夜間表演「{{Link-en|迪士尼之夢|Disney Dreams!|迪士尼之夢！}}」中也排入了艾莎的《放開手》<ref>{{cite news|last=Monti|first=Andrea|title=Disneyland Paris: Intervista a Katy Harris|url=http://www.parksmania.it/2013/11/26/intervista-katy/|accessdate=2013-12-14|newspaper=Parks Mania|date=2013-11-23|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214052516/http://www.parksmania.it/2013/11/26/intervista-katy|archivedate=2013-12-14}}</ref>，佛州迪士尼內的[[神奇王國|神奇王國]]也將類似的活動配在「{{Link-en|慶祝神奇|Celebrate the Magic}}」表演秀中，在艾莎唱歌之時還播放《冰雪奇緣》中的片段影像<ref>{{cite news|title='Frozen' Segment Added to 'Celebrate the Magic'|url=http://www.laughingplace.com/w/news/2013/11/21/frozen-segment-added-to-celebrate-the-magic/|accessdate=2013-12-14|newspaper=Laughing Place|date=2013-11-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151231043339/http://www.laughingplace.com/w/news/2013/11/21/frozen-segment-added-to-celebrate-the-magic/|archivedate=2015-12-31}}</ref>。

